1","parent":"132","text":"Diagnóstico","guid":"MKGv2R4IbZWnNrXKf4CJZg","children":[{"id":"162","parent":"161","text":"Elemento clave\\N→ osmolaridad","guid":"a7CV8F4d2vouI8H40H9P0g","children":[{"id":"163","parent":"162","text":"MOsm/kg= [(Na+ + K+) x 2 +  glicemia/18 + BUN/2,8]","guid":"oxwdldr-42x5mxDV2p5lEQ","children":[]},{"id":"164","parent":"162","text":"O la forma rápida el doble de la natremia","guid":"ACP7fQAR-VwdPd2aHBGL8g","children":[]}]},{"id":"165","parent":"161","text":"Criterios (6)","guid":"3sMiP784iooVLodqMe_7qw","children":[{"id":"166","parent":"165","text":"Glicemia >= 600","guid":"6iX3WY0zWXW0vebuf3bQPA","children":[]},{"id":"167","parent":"165","text":"Osmolaridad >= 320","guid":"4KMmdDGSv9sdvOIQy28RVw","children":[]},{"id":"168","parent":"165","text":"Ph > 7,3","guid":"MWgyUKz2dDmEctoC2_QTDg","children":[]},{"id":"169","parent":"165","text":"Hco3- >18","guid":"3PO2WABAbeYc_c4wIv95GQ","children":[]},{"id":"170","parent":"165","text":"Cetonuria negativa o levemente +","guid":"tj3MR0dwf3fRCxaDvbB-Sw","children":[]},{"id":"171","parent":"165","text":"Estatus mental en sopor o coma","guid":"VQ61IdZRz94cfNmiHxWxnA","children":[]}]},{"id":"172","parent":"161","text":"SHH se estima una pérdida de 100-200 ml de agua x kg\\Nde peso, 5-15 meq/kg de Na+ y Cl- y 4-6 meq/kg de K+","guid":"BnkgDp_xaLXIwmXcC_iOPg","children":[]}]},{"id":"173","parent":"132","text":"Tratamiento\\NTres pilares ","guid":"nvljS-BfnhKprpbYhWFG8g","children":[{"id":"174","parent":"173","text":"Hidratación","guid":"PTnoe5S3hqG6B9NdkDiyMg","children":[{"id":"175","parent":"174","text":"1 a 2lt la primera hora","guid":"VUqPppUhoasI50edqp80bg","children":[]},{"id":"176","parent":"174","text":"luego va a depender de la\\Nhidratación y diuresis","guid":"cAIR7F8e_En0Arl3daqSXQ","children":[{"id":"177","parent":"176","text":"Deficit de\\Nagua","guid":"578jertLYePOWNs3AXBa4w","children":[{"id":"178","parent":"177","text":"Agua  corporal  total  x  (1-(sodio target/sodio  medido)","guid":"6BL6tTMMasffRCAGDl2LVA","children":[]},{"id":"179","parent":"177","text":"coeficiente  en  adultos coeficiente:  0,6  para adultos,  0,5  para\\Nmujeres  y  hombre  viejos,  0,45 para  mujeres  de  edad avanzada.","guid":"1jgOExlq7sneh6MVgw77CQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"180","parent":"174","text":"pacientes mayores, por lo que debemos tener cuidado de  no volemizar demasiado rápido","guid":"IsCtK7dh0iNQCxnivP-B6w","children":[]}]},{"id":"181","parent":"173","text":"Reposición de K+","guid":"qeXay2FwLA3u03Ak6gfJHw","children":[{"id":"182","parent":"181","text":"No iniciar insulinoterapia mientras no se corroboren niveles de K+ para prevenir hipokalemia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"183","parent":"181","text":"Si K+ < 3,3 reponer K+ primero, no aportar insulina aún, aportar 20-30 meq/hora en solución fisiológica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"184","parent":"181","text":"Si K+ 3,3-5,3 dar 20-30 meq x litro de SF, mantener K+ entre 4 y 5","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"185","parent":"181","text":"Si K+ >= 5,3  no dar K+","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"186","parent":"173","text":"Insulina","guid":"L3Wty9SivaI2UbYBDV7s3A","children":[{"id":"187","parent":"186","text":"infusión continua ev a dosis 0,1 U/kg/hora, es discutible el uso de bolo ev al igual que en CAD.\\NReducción de glicemia debe ser de 50-70 mg/dl/hora, si no baja doblar la dosis.","guid":"jfOhPOn6U76kmMJiU_as5w","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"188","parent":"132","text":"Criterios de\\Nresolución (3)","guid":"liLnlTYZztBdpFPH9GoWzg","children":[{"id":"189","parent":"188","text":"Recuperación de conciencia","guid":"55Vjv_oeiBWdQffG6BL6rg","children":[]},{"id":"190","parent":"188","text":"Glicemia < 300","guid":"bTtTt46d8IiH9Equydhe6A","children":[]},{"id":"191","parent":"188","text":"Osmolaridad < 320","guid":"AvJF2Smj65vNeV80Av6D_A","children":[]}]},{"id":"192","parent":"132","text":"Complicaciones","guid":"KvhJj_r-pZ4QK7ocgBiGrA","children":[{"id":"193","parent":"192","text":"infecciones principalmente","guid":"sG-qleVRBG8Gs3jQdXaDng","children":[]},{"id":"194","parent":"192","text":"También edema cerebral, EPA, ACV.","guid":"XlzpPkkh7y3P6DPPcfPDig","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"195","parent":"0","text":"Tratamiento post\\Ncrisis hiperglicémica","guid":"9r_-MQfr78RcsuGsEjQTHA","children":[{"id":"196","parent":"195","text":"No realimentar antes de 48 hrs","guid":"udv4lPNwEZAsGm3Jf0O2AA","children":[]},{"id":"197","parent":"195","text":"Si glicemia <250 usar glucosado al 5% con insulina en dosis 0,1 a 0,15 U/kg/hora por cada 500ml de solución glucosada,\\Nla cual se ajusta según los controles de HGT cada  6 hrs subiendo o bajando entre 2 a 4 U.","guid":"5x0iv8MNhPr3pDDhRVCZow","children":[]},{"id":"198","parent":"195","text":"Para volver a esquema previo si usaba insulina se deja la dosis de los\\Nrequerimientos que tuvo las 24 hrs previa repartida en 2/3-1/3","guid":"4H78b1VRMcBXjczCcEgMtA","children":[]},{"id":"199","parent":"195","text":"Si no usaba insulina se recomienda mantener con insulina por un período acotado y después de eso\\Nse puede reevaluar la respuesta B insular midiendo péptido C y proceder de acuerdo a esto.","guid":"gn4xcLIcMJF3YeEza8yCdA","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":199,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"General","folder":"Entidades clínicas","filename":"- Complicaciones metabólicas agudas de la DM","id":"map_11","resolved_references":[],"title_raw":"- Complicaciones metabólicas agudas de la DM"}